        "TileImage": "$($repository 36eab2c5-79b3-4aca-bf8b-8b40ff64c3d5).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47, your destination is Sapienza Italy, where presidential candidate Marco Abiatti will be speaking. Your targets are members of his staff, who disagreeing with Abiatti&apos;s message plan to sabotage his campaign. Our client, Mr. Abiatti, after learning of their plot wants this insubordination to be put down swiftly, quietly, and lethally. I will leave you to prepare.",
